column2: "I did not come here intentionally. When I had come to, I was here."
"There have been many reports, I supposed I've been brought here this time."
"Even so, I have been searching for this place, so this outcome is fortunate."
"It seems that nine times out of ten, it's either Darkers, or that mysterious person."
"Though admittedly, I have no interest in their objectives in creating this imitation."
"What has caught my attention is the reports of Dark Falz being sighted in this area."
"I would like to verify those claims, that is all."
"I would like for you to accompany me, but you have no obligation to do so."
"I am not someone that merits such treatment."
"外伝 もうそこにいないわたし"
